TwitterTools
by @erikaheidi
http://erikafocke.com.br/twittertools

Lib PHP for using Twitter Api with OAuth

Files:
index.php - Posting and follow example
mentions.php - Get authenticated user mentions example
dms.php - Get authenticated user dms example
timeline.php - Get authenticated user timeline example
followers.php - Get any user followers example

style.css - just some css to make things sweeter

Directories
lib/ - classes OAuth, TwitterOAuth and TwitterTools
img/ - twitter sign up button

